  "texts": [
    "Additionally,, we have also shown the possibility of other possible NDN attacks on the suggested schemes.",
    "The research presented in this survey confirms the need for a more robust approach to preventing content poisoning attacks in NDN.",
    "Finally, some open research challenges have been added.",
    "Furthermore, this work hopes to inspire the NDN research community to make some visible progress on this front."
